having some trouble with Units. I wanted to use s^2 in an equation
but Units.py doesn't like it. Example below.
Thanks.

```
from PySpice.Unit import *
import traceback

try:
  COMPA = -3.318E-17@u_s^2
except:
  traceback.print_exc()

try:
  COMPA = -3.318E-17@u_s * 1.0@u_s
  print(COMPA)
